    <text type="letter">
        <body>

            <opener>
                <dateline>
                    <name type="place">431 Stevens Street <lb/>Camden New
                        Jersey</name>
                    <date when="1881-03-31">March 31 <choice>
                            <abbr>'81</abbr>
                            <expan>1881</expan>
                        </choice></date>
                </dateline>
                <salute>Dear Sir<ptr target="hyb.00012_n1"
                        />&#8212;</salute>
            </opener>

            <p>In compliance with your request in letter of 28th<ptr target="hyb.00012_n2"/> I this
                day send you by mail to same address as this card my two Volumes <hi rend="italic"
                    >Leaves of Grass</hi> and <hi rend="italic">Two Rivulets</hi> (<hi rend="italic">Memoranda of the
                    war</hi> embodied in latter <choice>
                    <abbr>Vol:</abbr><expan>Volume</expan></choice>) The price is &#36;10, which please send me here by p.o. order.</p>

            <closer>
                <signed rend="right">Walt Whitman</signed> 
            </closer>
        </body>
